file.name: schema.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
servers:
 - url: https://{environment}.osis.uclouvain.be/api/v1/learning_unit/
   variables:
     environment:
       default: dev
       enum:
         - dev # Development server
         - qa # Staging server
         - test # Test server
 - url: https://osis.uclouvain.be/api/v1/learning_unit/
   description: 'Production server'
info:
  version: '1.10'
  title: 'Learning Unit Service'
  description: |-
    A set of API endpoints that allow you to get information about learning unit
paths:
  /learning_units:
    get:
      description: Return a list of all the learning unit with optional filtering.
      operationId: learningunits_list
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: limit
          schema:
            description: Number of results to return per page.
            type: integer
        - in: query
          name: offset
          schema:
            description: The initial index from which to return the results.
            type: integer
        - in: query
          name: acronym
          schema:
            description: Filter acronym in exact match
            type: string
        - in: query
          name: acronym_like
          schema:
            description: Filter acronym in contains match case insensitive
            type: string
        - in: query
          name: year
          schema:
            type: integer
        - in: query
          name: lang
          schema:
            type: string
        - in: query
          name: campus
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: string
        - in: query
          name: stage_dimona
          schema:
            type: boolean
        # FIX ME: use explode: true instead of split
        - in: query
          name: learning_unit_codes
          schema:
            type: string
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/Accept-Language'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-FirstName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-LastName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-Email'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-GlobalID'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/PaginatedLearningUnitList'
        '400':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/BadRequest'
        '401':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Unauthorized'
      tags:
      - learning_units
  /learning_units/{year}/{acronym}:
    get:
      description: Return the detail of the learning unit
      operationId: learningunits_read
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: year
          required: true
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: integer
        - in: path
          name: acronym
          required: true
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: string
        - in: query
          name: lang
          schema:
            type: string
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/Accept-Language'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-FirstName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-LastName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-Email'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-GlobalID'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                oneOf:
                  - $ref: '#/components/schemas/LearningUnitDetailed'
                  - $ref: '#/components/schemas/ExternalLearningUnit'
        '400':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/BadRequest'
        '401':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Unauthorized'
        '404':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/NotFound'
      tags:
      - learning_units
  /learning_units/{year}/{acronym}/title:
    get:
      description: Return the title of the learning unit
      operationId: learningunitstitle_read
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: year
          required: true
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: integer
        - in: path
          name: acronym
          required: true
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: string
        - in: query
          name: lang
          schema:
            type: string
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/Accept-Language'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-FirstName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-LastName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-Email'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-GlobalID'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  title:
                    type: string
        '400':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/BadRequest'
        '401':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Unauthorized'
        '404':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/NotFound'
      tags:
        - learning_units
  /learning_units/{year}/{acronym}/classes:
    get:
      description: Return the classes of the learning unit
      operationId: get_learning_unit_classes
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: year
          required: true
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: integer
        - in: path
          name: acronym
          required: true
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: string
        - in: query
          name: lang
          schema:
            type: string
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/Accept-Language'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-FirstName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-LastName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-Email'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-GlobalID'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/EffectiveClass'
        '400':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/BadRequest'
        '401':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Unauthorized'
        '404':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/NotFound'
      tags:
        - learning_units
  /learning_units/{year}/{acronym}/attributions:
    get:
      description: Return all attributions assign to the learning unit
      operationId: learningunitattributions_read
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: year
          required: true
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: integer
        - in: path
          name: acronym
          required: true
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: string
        - in: query
          name: lang
          schema:
            type: string
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/Accept-Language'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-FirstName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-LastName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-Email'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-GlobalID'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/LearningUnitAttribution'
        '400':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/BadRequest'
        '401':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Unauthorized'
        '404':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/NotFound'
      tags:
      - learning_units
  /learning_units/{year}/{acronym}/education_group_roots:
    get:
      description: Return all education groups root which utilize the learning unit specified
      operationId: learningunitutilization_read
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: year
          required: true
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: integer
        - in: path
          name: acronym
          required: true
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: string
        - in: query
          name: lang
          schema:
            type: string
        - in: query
          name: ignore_complementary_module
          schema:
            description: True if we want to filter roots if the learning unit is inside a complementary module behind the root. By default, all roots of the learning unit are returned.
            type: boolean
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/Accept-Language'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-FirstName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-LastName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-Email'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-GlobalID'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/EducationGroupRoot'
        '400':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/BadRequest'
        '401':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Unauthorized'
        '404':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/NotFound'
      tags:
      - learning_units
  /learning_units/{year}/{acronym}/achievements:
    get:
      description: Return all achievement in order according of the learning unit specified.
      operationId: learningunitachievements_read
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: year
          required: true
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: integer
        - in: path
          name: acronym
          required: true
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: string
        - in: query
          name: lang
          schema:
            type: string
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/Accept-Language'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-FirstName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-LastName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-Email'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-GlobalID'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/LearningUnitAchievement'
        '400':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/BadRequest'
        '401':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Unauthorized'
        '404':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/NotFound'
      tags:
      - learning_units
  /learning_units/{year}/{acronym}/summary_specification:
    get:
      description: Return all summary and specification information of the learning unit specified
      operationId: learningunitsummaryspecification_read
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: year
          required: true
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: integer
        - in: path
          name: acronym
          required: true
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: string
        - in: query
          name: lang
          schema:
            type: string
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/Accept-Language'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-FirstName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-LastName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-Email'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-GlobalID'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/LearningUnitSummarySpecification'
        '400':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/BadRequest'
        '401':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Unauthorized'
        '404':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/NotFound'
      tags:
      - learning_units
  /learning_units/{year}/{acronym}/prerequisites:
    get:
      description: Returns all education groups for which this learning unit year had prerequisites
      operationId: learningunitprerequisites_read
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: year
          required: true
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: integer
        - in: path
          name: acronym
          required: true
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: string
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/Accept-Language'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-FirstName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-LastName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-Email'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-GlobalID'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/LearningUnitPrerequisite'
        '400':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/BadRequest'
        '401':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Unauthorized'
        '404':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/NotFound'
      tags:
      - learning_units
  /learning_units/{year}/{acronym}/teaching_materials:
    get:
      description: Return all teaching materials of the learning unit
      operationId: learningunitteachingmaterials_read
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: year
          required: true
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: integer
        - in: path
          name: acronym
          required: true
          schema:
            description: ''
            type: string
        - in: query
          name: lang
          schema:
            type: string
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/Accept-Language'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-FirstName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-LastName'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-Email'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/X-User-GlobalID'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/LearningUnitTeachingMaterial'
        '400':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/BadRequest'
        '401':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/Unauthorized'
        '404':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/NotFound'
      tags:
        - learning_units
components:
  securitySchemes:
    Token:
      type: apiKey
      in: header
      name: Authorization
      description: Enter your token in the format **Token <token>**
  parameters:
    X-User-FirstName:
      in: header
      name: X-User-FirstName
      schema:
        type: string
      required: false
    X-User-LastName:
      in: header
      name: X-User-LastName
      schema:
        type: string
      required: false
    X-User-Email:
      in: header
      name: X-User-Email
      schema:
        type: string
      required: false
    X-User-GlobalID:
      in: header
      name: X-User-GlobalID
      schema:
        type: string
      required: false
    Accept-Language:
      in: header
      name: Accept-Language
      description: >
        The header advertises which languages the client is able to understand, and which locale variant is preferred. (By languages, we mean natural languages, such as English, and not programming languages.)
      schema:
        $ref: '#/components/schemas/AcceptedLanguageEnum'
      required: false
  responses:
    Unauthorized:
      description: Unauthorized
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
    BadRequest:
      description: Bad request
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
    NotFound:
      description: The specified resource was not found
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
  schemas:
    PaginatedLearningUnitList:
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pagination'
        - type: object
          properties:
            results:
              type: array
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/LearningUnit'
    Pagination:
      type: object
      properties:
        count:
          type: integer
        next:
          type: string
          format: uri
          nullable: true
        previous:
          type: string
          format: uri
          nullable: true
    LearningUnit:
      type: object
      properties:
        url:
          type: string
          format: uri
        osis_url:
          type: string
          format: uri
        acronym:
          type: string
        credits:
          type: string
        status:
          type: boolean
        has_proposal:
          type: boolean
          nullable: true
        has_classes:
          type: boolean
        title:
          type: string
        type:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/LearningUnitTypeEnum'
        type_text:
          type: string
        subtype:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/LearningUnitSubtypeEnum'
        subtype_text:
          type: string
        requirement_entity:
          type: string
        allocation_entity:
          type: string
        allocation_faculty:
          type: string
        academic_year:
          type: integer
          example: 2014
    LearningUnitDetailed:
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/LearningUnit'
        - type: object
          properties:
            credits:
              type: number
              multipleOf: 0.01
            quadrimester:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/QuadrimesterEnum'
            quadrimester_text:
              type: string
            periodicity:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/PeriodicityEnum'
            periodicity_text:
              type: string
            campus:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/LearningUnitCampus'
            components:
              type: array
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/LearningUnitComponent'
            partims:
              type: array
              items:
                type: string
                format: uri
            parent:
              type: string
              format: uri
            team:
              type: boolean
            language:
              type: string
              description: |
                The language code according to ISO 639-1 specification (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_ISO_639-1_codes)
            french_friendly:
              type: boolean
            english_friendly:
              type: boolean
            exchange_students:
              type: boolean
            proposal:
              type: object
              properties:
                folder:
                  type: string
                type:
                  type: string
                status:
                  type: string
            summary_status:
              type: string
            professional_integration:
              type: boolean
            remark:
              type: string
            remark_en:
              type: string
    ExternalLearningUnit:
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/LearningUnitDetailed'
        - type: object
          properties:
            local_code:
              type: string
            local_url:
              type: string
              format: uri
    EffectiveClass:
      type: object
      properties:
        code:
          type: string
          example: 'Z'
        full_code:
          type: string
          example: 'LDROI1001_Z'
        title_fr:
          type: string
        title_en:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        teaching_place_uuid:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        campus_name:
          type: string
        organization_name:
          type: string
        derogation_quadrimester:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/QuadrimesterEnum'
        derogation_quadrimester_text:
          type: string
        session_derogation:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        volume_q1:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        volume_q2:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        type:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ComponentTypeEnum'
        type_text:
          type: string
    LearningUnitComponent:
      type: object
      properties:
        type:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ComponentTypeEnum'
        type_text:
          type: string
        planned_classes:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        hourly_volume_total_annual:
          type: number
          multipleOf: 0.01
        hourly_volume_total_annual_computed:
          type: number
          multipleOf: 0.01
    LearningUnitCampus:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        organization:
          type: string
        organization_url:
          type: string
          format: uri
    LearningUnitAttribution:
      type: object
      properties:
        email:
          type: string
          format: email
        function:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/AttributionFunctionEnum'
        function_text:
          type: string
        global_id:
          type: string
        last_name:
          type: string
        middle_name:
          type: string
        first_name:
          type: string
        substitute:
          type: object
          properties:
            email:
              type: string
              format: email
            global_id:
              type: string
            last_name:
              type: string
            middle_name:
              type: string
            first_name:
              type: string
    EducationGroupRoot:
      type: object
      properties:
        url:
          type: string
          format: uri
        acronym:
          type: string
        code:
          type: string
        credits:
          type: number
          multipleOf: 0.01
        title:
          type: string
        decree_category:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/DecreeCategoryEnum'
        decree_category_text:
          type: string
        duration:
          type: integer
          minimum: 1
        duration_unit:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/DurationUnitEnum'
        duration_unit_text:
          type: string
        education_group_type:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/EducationGroupTypeEnum'
        education_group_type_text:
          type: string
        academic_year:
          type: number
          example: 2014
        learning_unit_credits:
          type: number
          multipleOf: 0.01
    LearningUnitAchievement:
      type: object
      properties:
        code_name:
          type: string
          example: '1.0'
        achievement:
          type: string
    LearningUnitSummarySpecification:
      type: object
      properties:
        bibliography:
          type: string
        resume:
          type: string
        evaluation_methods:
          type: string
        other_informations:
          type: string
        online_resources:
          type: string
        teaching_methods:
          type: string
        themes_discussed:
          type: string
        prerequisite:
          type: string
        mobility:
          type: string
        teaching_methods_force_majeure:
          type: string
        evaluation_methods_force_majeure:
          type: string
        other_informations_force_majeure:
          type: string
      required:
        - bibliography
        - resume
        - evaluation_methods
        - other_informations
        - online_resources
        - teaching_methods
        - themes_discussed
        - prerequisite
        - mobility
        - teaching_methods_force_majeure
        - evaluation_methods_force_majeure
        - other_informations_force_majeure
    LearningUnitPrerequisite:
      type: object
      properties:
        url:
          type: string
          format: uri
        title:
          type: string
        acronym:
          type: string
        code:
          type: string
        education_group_type:
          type: string
        education_group_type_text:
          type: string
        academic_year:
          type: integer
        prerequisites:
          type: string
    LearningUnitTeachingMaterial:
      type: array
      items:
        type: object
        properties:
          title:
            type: string
          mandatory:
            type: boolean
    LearningUnitTypeEnum:
      type: string
      enum:
        - 'COURSE'
        - 'INTERNSHIP'
        - 'DISSERTATION'
        - 'OTHER_COLLECTIVE'
        - 'OTHER_INDIVIDUAL'
        - 'MASTER_THESIS'
        - 'EXTERNAL'
    LearningUnitSubtypeEnum:
      type: string
      enum:
        - 'FULL'
        - 'PARTIM'
    QuadrimesterEnum:
      type: string
      nullable: true
      enum:
        - 'Q1'
        - 'Q2'
        - 'Q3'
        - 'Q1and2'
        - 'Q1or2'
    PeriodicityEnum:
      type: string
      enum:
        - 'ANNUAL'
        - 'BIENNIAL_EVEN'
        - 'BIENNIAL_ODD'
    ComponentTypeEnum:
      type: string
      enum:
        - 'LECTURING'
        - 'PRACTICAL_EXERCISES'
    AttributionFunctionEnum:
      type: string
      enum:
        - 'COORDINATOR'
        - 'HOLDER'
        - 'CO_HOLDER'
        - 'DEPUTY'
        - 'DEPUTY_AUTHORITY'
        - 'DEPUTY_SABBATICAL'
        - 'DEPUTY_TEMPORARY'
        - 'PROFESSOR'
        - 'INTERNSHIP_SUPERVISOR'
        - 'INTERNSHIP_CO_SUPERVISOR'
        - 'DEPUTY_DISEASE_OR_MATERNITY'
    DecreeCategoryEnum:
      type: string
      enum:
        - 'FCONT'
        - 'DOC'
        - 'BAC'
        - 'MA1'
        - 'MA2X'
        - 'MA2D'
        - 'MA2S'
        - 'MA2A'
        - 'MA2M'
        - 'MACO'
        - 'AESSB'
        - 'CAPS'
        - 'FODO'
        - 'DOCB'
        - 'CEMC'
    DurationUnitEnum:
      type: string
      enum:
        - 'QUADRIMESTER'
        - 'TRIMESTER'
        - 'MONTH'
        - 'WEEK'
        - 'DAY'
    EducationGroupTypeEnum:
      type: string
      enum:
        - 'AGGREGATION'
        - 'CERTIFICATE_OF_PARTICIPATION'
        - 'CERTIFICATE_OF_SUCCESS'
        - 'CERTIFICATE_OF_HOLDING_CREDITS'
        - 'BACHELOR'
        - 'CERTIFICATE'
        - 'CAPAES'
        - 'RESEARCH_CERTIFICATE'
        - 'UNIVERSITY_FIRST_CYCLE_CERTIFICATE'
        - 'UNIVERSITY_SECOND_CYCLE_CERTIFICATE'
        - 'ACCESS_CONTEST'
        - 'LANGUAGE_CLASS'
        - 'ISOLATED_CLASS'
        - 'PHD'
        - 'FORMATION_PHD'
        - 'JUNIOR_YEAR'
        - 'PGRM_MASTER_120'
        - 'MASTER_MA_120'
        - 'MASTER_MD_120'
        - 'MASTER_MS_120'
        - 'PGRM_MASTER_180_240'
        - 'MASTER_MA_180_240'
